---
import { controls } from '../consts';
---

{/* ===== How to Play ===== */}
<section class="border-t border-white/5 py-24">
  <p class="eyebrow">How to Play</p>
  <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold text-rb-muted sm:text-4xl">Space と Shift の 2 キー</h2>
  <div class="mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-white/10">
    <table class="w-full text-left">
      <tbody>
        {
          controls.map((c) => (
            <tr class="border-b border-white/5 last:border-0">
              <th class="w-40 bg-white/5 px-5 py-4 font-mono text-rb-core">{c.key}</th>
              <td class="px-5 py-4">{c.desc}</td>
            </tr>
          ))
        }
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-rb-muted/70">
    物理メモ: 軌道は角運動量保存（&omega; = L / r&sup2;）。半径を縮めるほど速く回る。
    Web 版はタッチ / ポインタ操作にも対応。
  </p>

  {/* Space=縮小 / Shift=拡大 の対比図解 */}
  <figure class="mt-10">
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {/* Space: 軌道半径を縮小 → 高速回転 */}
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/5 p-5">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-rb-core">SPACE — 縮小</p>
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 200 160"
          class="mt-3 block h-auto w-full"
          role="img"
          aria-label="Space キーで軌道半径を縮小すると角速度が上がる図"
        >
          {/* 外側の元軌道 (薄い破線) */}
          <circle
            cx="100"
            cy="80"
            r="55"
            fill="none"
            stroke="var(--color-rb-core)"
            stroke-opacity="0.2"
            stroke-width="1"
            stroke-dasharray="3 4"
          />
          {/* 縮小後軌道 */}
          <circle
            cx="100"
            cy="80"
            r="32"
            fill="none"
            stroke="var(--color-rb-core)"
            stroke-opacity="0.5"
            stroke-width="1"
            stroke-dasharray="3 4"
          />
          {/* 内向き矢印 (半径方向) */}
          <g stroke="var(--color-rb-core)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none">
            <path d="M155 80 L132 80" marker-end="url(#arrow-cyan)" />
            <path d="M45 80 L68 80" marker-end="url(#arrow-cyan)" />
          </g>
          {/* Core */}
          <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="6" fill="var(--color-rb-core)" />
          {/* Shield (内側軌道上) */}
          <circle cx="132" cy="80" r="5" fill="var(--color-rb-shield)" />
          {/* 角速度ラベル */}
          <g font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace" font-size="11">
            <text x="100" y="148" fill="var(--color-rb-combo)" text-anchor="middle">&#969; 大 (速い)</text>
          </g>
          <defs>
            <marker
              id="arrow-cyan"
              viewBox="0 0 10 10"
              refX="8"
              refY="5"
              markerWidth="6"
              markerHeight="6"
              orient="auto-start-reverse"
            >
              <path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="var(--color-rb-core)" />
            </marker>
          </defs>
        </svg>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-rb-muted/80">
          軌道半径 <span class="text-rb-core">r</span> が小さくなり、角速度 <span class="text-rb-combo">&omega;</span> が上がる。
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Shift: 軌道半径を拡大 → 低速回転 */}
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/5 p-5">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-rb-shield">SHIFT — 拡大</p>
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 200 160"
          class="mt-3 block h-auto w-full"
          role="img"
          aria-label="Shift キーで軌道半径を拡大すると角速度が下がる図"
        >
          {/* 内側の元軌道 (薄い破線) */}
          <circle
            cx="100"
            cy="80"
            r="32"
            fill="none"
            stroke="var(--color-rb-shield)"
            stroke-opacity="0.2"
            stroke-width="1"
            stroke-dasharray="3 4"
          />
          {/* 拡大後軌道 */}
          <circle
            cx="100"
            cy="80"
            r="55"
            fill="none"
            stroke="var(--color-rb-shield)"
            stroke-opacity="0.5"
            stroke-width="1"
            stroke-dasharray="3 4"
          />
          {/* 外向き矢印 (半径方向) */}
          <g stroke="var(--color-rb-shield)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none">
            <path d="M132 80 L155 80" marker-end="url(#arrow-magenta)" />
            <path d="M68 80 L45 80" marker-end="url(#arrow-magenta)" />
          </g>
          {/* Core */}
          <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="6" fill="var(--color-rb-core)" />
          {/* Shield (外側軌道上) */}
          <circle cx="155" cy="80" r="5" fill="var(--color-rb-shield)" />
          {/* 角速度ラベル */}
          <g font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace" font-size="11">
            <text x="100" y="148" fill="var(--color-rb-muted)" text-anchor="middle">&#969; 小 (遅い)</text>
          </g>
          <defs>
            <marker
              id="arrow-magenta"
              viewBox="0 0 10 10"
              refX="8"
              refY="5"
              markerWidth="6"
              markerHeight="6"
              orient="auto-start-reverse"
            >
              <path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="var(--color-rb-shield)" />
            </marker>
          </defs>
        </svg>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-rb-muted/80">
          軌道半径 <span class="text-rb-shield">r</span> が大きくなり、角速度 <span class="text-rb-muted">&omega;</span> が下がる。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <figcaption class="mt-3 text-center text-sm text-rb-muted/70">
      角運動量保存 &omega; = L / r&sup2; — r を能動的に変えてタイミングを作る。
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
</section>
